title: Spacious Floorplans, Gorgeous Views, Call TODAY!
posting_body: ['Fun in the Sun', 'LIFE ON THE WATER', 'A BOLD URBAN LIFESTYLE', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Lakefront on Washington', '538 Lakeside Avenue South, Seattle, WA, 98144', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 950 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Live life on the lake.', 'Located in the desirable Leschi neighborhood, Lakefront on Washington gives you unlimited access to serene water views, nearby trails, and local eats, as well as the sights and sounds of downtown Seattle.', 'Find an ideal studio, one, or two bedroom apartment designed to match your outdoor enthusiasm and busy routine, and feast your eyes on features like stainless-steel appliances, wood-style flooring, and jaw-dropping views from oversized windows.', 'Sophisticated amenities, high-end finishes, and an ideal location on the west shore make Lakefront on Washington your ideal base camp for life in the Pacific Northwest.', 'Features', '- White Quartz Countertops', '- Views of Lake Washington, Mount Rainier, Downtown Bellevue & the Cascade Mountains*', '- Private Patio or Balcony', '- Enlarged Windows', '- Stainless-Steel Appliances', '- Undermount Sinks', '- Roller Shades', '- Marine-Inspired Backsplashes', '- Wood-Burning Fireplace*', '- Tile & Wood-Style Flooring', '- Dishwasher', '- Wood-Finished Cabinetry', '- Microwaves', '*In Select Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Barbecue Grilling Stations', '- Business Center', '- Online Rental Payments', '- Onsite Recycling Program', '- Onsite Management', '- Lake Washington Swim Platform', '- Swimming Pool w/ Sundeck', '- Onsite Moorage w/ Rentable Boat Slips', '- Green-Friendly Community', '- Multiple Clothing Care Centers', '- Close to Parks', '- State-of-the-Art Fitness Center', '- Lake Access', '- Composting Program', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'Tx8mgyVHl4']
